{"id":"mess","term":"Mess","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>A portion of food given to a guest (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 43:34\">Gen. 43:34</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Samuel 11:8\">2 Sam. 11:8</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Genesis 43:34","2 Samuel 11:8"]}